OL,3,CMan found guilty of raping woman in
OL,4,Cportable toilet on seafront
OL,6,FA man from Syria has been found guilty
OL,7,Fof raping a 19-year-old woman in a
OL,8,Fportable toilet on Bournemouth
OL,9,Fseafront.
OL,11,FMohammed Abdulla from West Drayton
OL,12,Fattacked the woman in July last year
OL,13,Fas she was walking home after losing
OL,14,Fcontact with her friends on a night
OL,15,Fout.
OL,17,FAfter a trial lasting eight days, the
OL,18,Fjury of five men and seven women took
OL,19,Fjust 3 hours to find Abdullah guilty
OL,20,Fof rape and assault by penetration at
OL,21,FBournemouth Crown Court.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
