PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1778922392
OL,3,CMan found guilty of raping woman in
OL,4,Cportable toilet on seafront
OL,6,FHis victim and her family have been in
OL,7,Fcourt most days and sobbed as the jury
OL,8,Fforeman announced the verdict.
OL,10,FSpeaking through an interpreter, 19-
OL,11,Fyear-old Abdullah had told the jury
OL,12,Fthat sex with the woman was consensual.
OL,14,FHowever, the jury was shown evidence
OL,15,Fof multiple bruises and ripped
OL,16,Fclothing from the assault.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
