PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1778922392
OL,3,CMan found guilty of raping woman in
OL,4,Cportable toilet on seafront
OL,6,FThe woman had been separated from a
OL,7,Ffriend after a night out in
OL,8,FBournemouth on July 6, 2025. Because
OL,9,Fher phone had no charge, she had
OL,10,Fdecided to walk home to Christchurch
OL,11,Falong the seafront.
OL,13,FThe court heard that Abdullah offered
OL,14,Fto take the woman home on his Beryl
OL,15,Fbike, but minutes later he sexually
OL,16,Fassaulted her and then carried her
OL,17,Finto a portable toilet on the seafront
OL,18,Fwhere he raped her.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
