PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1778922392
OL,3,CMan found guilty of raping woman in
OL,4,Cportable toilet on seafront
OL,6,FMohammed Abdullah arrived from Syria
OL,7,Fin 2023, and has permanent leave to
OL,8,Fremain under the family reunion
OL,9,Fscheme. He had been studying English
OL,10,Fand training to be a barber.
OL,12,FHe showed no emotion as the guilty
OL,13,Fverdict was delivered.
OL,15,FJudge Robert Pawson warned the
OL,16,Fdefendant he faces a jail term as he
OL,17,Fremanded him in custody until the
OL,18,Fsentencing hearing on July 3 and
OL,19,Fordered a probation report to be
OL,20,Fprepared.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
