PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1778922392
OL,3,CMan found guilty of raping woman in
OL,4,Cportable toilet on seafront
OL,6,FHe told Abdullah: "On the 5th to 6th
OL,7,FJuly, having come down from London
OL,8,Fwith a group of other young men, by
OL,9,Funfortunate circumstances your path
OL,10,Fcrossed (with the complainant).
OL,12,F"She had had far too much to drink, it
OL,13,Fwas late at night, she was at the
OL,14,Fbeachfront at Bournemouth and, on a
OL,15,Fwhim, you decided to take advantage of
OL,16,Fthat.
OL,18,F"You deliberately took her further up
OL,19,Fthe beach to the Portaloos which, in
OL,20,Fmy judgment on the evidence, you knew
OL,21,Fwere there and knew they were open.
OL,26,@nD@SOUtD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
