CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1778922392
OL,3,CMan found guilty of raping woman in
OL,4,Cportable toilet on seafront
OL,6,F"You locked her in a Portaloo and you
OL,7,Fraped her.
OL,9,F"The sentence is to be decided on the
OL,10,F3rd July but it will inevitably
OL,11,Finvolve immediate custody."
